<P>It is our vision to be the <B>leading provider of Information Technology
solutions</B> in the industry, assuring that our customers succeed in the
ever-evolving world of information management</TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT">
<TD COLSPAN="5" HEIGHT="30"></TD></TR>
