ALT="Picture" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT">
<TD></TD>
<TD WIDTH="253" COLSPAN="4"><P><!-- Start of Text object --></P>

<P>It is AST&#146;s mission to be <B>the most responsive company</B> in
the world at providing superior computing solutions. We are committed to
surpassing customer expectations by providing innovative, high quality technology
and exceptional service in a convenient and timely manner. Through the dedication
and energy of our employees, we aspire to be the company that customers
choose to work with and proudly recommend.</TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT">
<TD COLSPAN="5" HEIGHT="27"></TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT">
<TD HEIGHT="40"></TD>
<TD WIDTH="253" COLSPAN="4"><IMG SRC="assets/images/core_values.GIF" HEIGHT="38" WIDTH="189" BORDER=
"0" ALT="Picture" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT">
<TD></TD>
<TD WIDTH="250"><P><!-- Start of Text object --></P>

<P>The employees of AST are driven by an <B>enthusiastic commitment to our
customers</B>. We are <B>determined</B> and <B>creative</B> in our pursuit
of <B>excellence</B> in everything we do. The <B>integrity</B> of our employees
and the <B>mutual respect</B> shown to customers, vendors and each other
are the foundations of our company. These values provide an environment
that fosters <B>pride</B> in each of our contributions to the continuing
success of AST.</TD>
<TD COLSPAN="3"></TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT">
<TD COLSPAN="5" HEIGHT="30"></TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT">
<TD HEIGHT="40"></TD>
<TD WIDTH="253" COLSPAN="4"><IMG SRC="assets/images/golas.GIF" HEIGHT="38" WIDTH="189" BORDER="0" ALT=
"Picture" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT">
<TD></TD>
<TD WIDTH="251" COLSPAN="2"><P><!-- Start of Text object --></P>

<P>Our foremost goals are <B>profitability</B> and achieving complete <B>customer
satisfaction</B> both internally for our employees as well as externally
for our clients and strategic business partners.</TD>
<TD COLSPAN="2"></TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT">
<TD COLSPAN="5" HEIGHT="25"></TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT">
<TD HEIGHT="41"></TD>
<TD WIDTH="253" COLSPAN="4"><IMG SRC="assets/images/management_principle.GIF" HEIGHT="38" WIDTH="189"
BORDER="0" ALT="Picture" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></TD></TR>
<TR VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT">
<TD></TD>
<TD WIDTH="252" COLSPAN="3"><P><!-- Start of Text object --></P>

<P>Speed Management: This principle is central to success in the extremely
competitive and rapidly-changing world of high technology. It requires the
disciplines of efficient time management, cost effective use of all resources,
cross-functional communications and employee empowerment. The result is
management&#146;s ability to make multiple critical business decisions more
quickly and with a higher percentage of accuracy than the competition.</TD>
